response.overview: When New Orleans Police Detective Danny Fisher stops a brilliant thief from getting away with a multimillion-dollar heist, the thief's girlfriend is accidentally killed. After escaping from prison, the criminal mastermind enacts his revenge, taunting Danny with 12 rounds of near-impossible puzzles and tasks that he must somehow complete to save the life of the woman he loves.
response.tagline: Can you survive 12 rounds for the one you love?
response.title: 12 Rounds

titles.title: ฝ่าวิกฤติ 12 รอบระห่ำนรก
